  "texts": [
    "Transformer also shows a stable weekly forecasting ability.",
    "When considering the hybrid models, three combinations of CNN and LSTM did not enhance the prediction abilities in this task.",
    "Despite the attractiveness of hybridizing the benefits of CNN and LSTM, the results did not find notable advantages for soil moisture prediction in terms of accuracy and computational costs.",
    "However, the feature attention mechanism has a constant positive effect on LSTM, whereas temporal attention mechanisms have little significance.",
    "In addition, incorporating generative adversarial network structures and training strategies into LSTM models (GAN-LSTM) has been found to improve prediction accuracy, especially in 7 d predictions."
